Deprecated API

Deprecated Classes
net.infonode.tabbedpanel.border.TabLineBorder
          As of ITP 1.2.0 use TabAreaLineBorder instead with TabbedPanelProperties.TAB_SPACING set to -1. 
 

Deprecated Methods

net.infonode.docking.properties.WindowTabButtonProperties.removeSuperObject()
          Use WindowTabButtonProperties.removeSuperObject(WindowTabButtonProperties) instead. 
net.infonode.docking.properties.WindowBarProperties.removeSuperObject()
          Use WindowBarProperties.removeSuperObject(WindowBarProperties) instead. 
net.infonode.docking.properties.ViewProperties.removeSuperObject()
          Use ViewProperties.removeSuperObject(ViewProperties) instead. 
net.infonode.docking.properties.TabWindowProperties.removeSuperObject()
          Use TabWindowProperties.removeSuperObject(TabWindowProperties) instead. 
net.infonode.docking.properties.SplitWindowProperties.removeSuperObject()
          Use SplitWindowProperties.removeSuperObject(SplitWindowProperties) instead. 
net.infonode.docking.properties.RootWindowProperties.removeSuperObject()
          Use RootWindowProperties.removeSuperObject(RootWindowProperties) instead. 
net.infonode.docking.properties.DockingWindowProperties.removeSuperObject()
          Use DockingWindowProperties.removeSuperObject(DockingWindowProperties) instead. 
 

Deprecated Constructors

          Use TabDragEvent.TabDragEvent(Object, java.awt.event.MouseEvent) instead.
